OL,3,CBlue Islands' suspension of operations
OL,4,C'a shambles', says travel expert
OL,6,FTravel expert Simon Calder has branded
OL,7,FBlue Islands' sudden cancellation of
OL,8,Fall flights "a shambles" and
OL,9,FLoganair's subsequent takeover of the
OL,10,Fcollapsed airline's routes as
OL,11,F"unseemly".
OL,13,FOn Friday evening, ITV News learned
OL,14,Fthat Blue Islands was on the brink of
OL,15,Fcollapse, with the airline announcing
OL,16,Fjust before 10pm that it had suspended
OL,17,Fits operations with immediate effect.
