OL,3,CBlue Islands' suspension of operations
OL,4,C'a shambles', says travel expert
OL,6,FWithin ten hours of this announcement,
OL,7,FLoganair revealed it would be offering
OL,8,F'rescue fares' for stranded
OL,9,Fpassengers, and was planning to
OL,10,F"establish a new permanent operating
OL,11,Fbase in Jersey".
OL,13,FBy the end of Saturday, Loganair had
OL,14,Fbegun selling tickets for flights
OL,15,Fbetween Jersey and Guernsey, as well
OL,16,Fas to Southampton, Exeter, and
OL,17,FBristol, into the New Year.
