OL,3,CBlue Islands' suspension of operations
OL,4,C'a shambles', says travel expert
OL,6,FOn Monday, Jersey's government
OL,7,Fannounced that Blue Islands had
OL,8,Fdecided to go into liquidation.
OL,10,FThe company still owes them #9.1
OL,11,Fmillion, including #1.7 million that
OL,12,Fwas loaned within the last two months.
OL,14,FThe Government will also pay up to
OL,15,F#1.5 million to Loganair to
OL,16,F"accelerate their full entry" into
OL,17,Foffering sustainable air links.
