OL,3,CBlue Islands' suspension of operations
OL,4,C'a shambles', says travel expert
OL,6,FMr Calder believes this transition
OL,7,Fcould have been conducted in a
OL,8,Fsmoother manner, despite the
OL,9,Foutstanding financial difficulties
OL,10,FBlue Islands faced, which would have
OL,11,Fallowed prebooked flights and tickets
OL,12,Fto still be honoured.
OL,14,FHe adds: "Suddenly to see all flights
OL,15,Fgrounded, and then a scramble to
OL,16,Freplace these routes - it isn't a good
OL,17,Flook from the UK.
