OL,3,CBlue Islands' suspension of operations
OL,4,C'a shambles', says travel expert
OL,6,F"I think it's a great shame, given the
OL,7,Fclose-knit nature of aviation and the
OL,8,FChannel Islands, that a gentler way
OL,9,Fwas not found to deal with what was
OL,10,Fundoubtedly a problem."
OL,12,FMr Calder has also pointed out that
OL,13,FLoganair will immediately face higher
OL,14,Foperational costs in the Channel
OL,15,FIslands than Blue Islands did, because
OL,16,Fthe company adheres to EU and UK
OL,17,Fcompensation rules.
