OL,3,CBlue Islands' suspension of operations
OL,4,C'a shambles', says travel expert
OL,6,FThis offers passengers greater
OL,7,Fprotection if their flight is delayed
OL,8,For cancelled, including up to #220
OL,9,Fcompensation for short-haul services
OL,10,Fwhich are significantly pushed back
OL,11,Fwhen the airline is at fault.
OL,13,FThey will also have to cover expenses
OL,14,Ffor long delays, regardless of the
OL,15,Freason.
OL,17,FMr Calder says: "If I fly to Jersey
OL,18,Fusing Loganair, and I can't get back
OL,19,Fbecause of fog, Loganair has to find
OL,20,Fme a hotel and give me all of my meals
OL,21,Fand that'll cost a bit."
